@claimsHost = http://localhost:5001
@notificationHost = http://localhost:5002
@documentHost = http://localhost:5003

### =====================
### Claims Service
### =====================

### Submit claim
POST {{claimsHost}}/claims
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "customerId": "d9f4cb92-a4b3-4cc6-a8f8-d36f4745af10",
  "policyId": "6d2c5d08-c7cf-4f4e-9b2f-ec4a4c3e32ec",
  "claimAmount": 1250.75
}

### Claims health
GET {{claimsHost}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Claims liveness
GET {{claimsHost}}/live
Accept: application/json

### Claims readiness
GET {{claimsHost}}/ready
Accept: application/json

### Claims metrics (Prometheus)
GET {{claimsHost}}/metrics
Accept: text/plain

### Claims Swagger JSON (development)
GET {{claimsHost}}/swagger/v1/swagger.json
Accept: application/json

### =====================
### Document Service
### =====================

### Generate upload URL
# @name generateUploadUrl
POST {{documentHost}}/documents/upload-url
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "claimId": "11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111",
  "documentType": "invoice",
  "fileName": "invoice-123.pdf"
}

### Upload document to pre-signed URL from previous response
PUT {{generateUploadUrl.response.body.$.uploadUrl}}
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

< ./infrastructure/docs/Workflow-diagram.md

### Document Swagger JSON (development)
GET {{documentHost}}/swagger/v1/swagger.json
Accept: application/json

### =====================
### Notification Service
### =====================

### Notification health
GET {{notificationHost}}/health
Accept: application/json

### Notification liveness
GET {{notificationHost}}/live
Accept: application/json

### Notification readiness
GET {{notificationHost}}/ready
Accept: application/json

### Notification metrics (Prometheus)
GET {{notificationHost}}/metrics
Accept: text/plain

### Notification Swagger JSON
GET {{notificationHost}}/swagger/v1/swagger.json
Accept: application/json
